988
01:03:41,143 --> 01:03:43,185
Yeah, I remember your mother.

989
01:03:44,268 --> 01:03:46,435
She had the same big smile...

990
01:03:46,477 --> 01:03:48,644
and the same dark hair.

991
01:03:48,727 --> 01:03:52,644
She had no nail on her little finger.
I don't remember why.

992
01:03:54,685 --> 01:03:58,228
A brick fell on it when she was little.
It never grew back.

993
01:03:58,311 --> 01:04:00,479
You see?
We have much history together.

994
01:04:00,519 --> 01:04:02,479
