995
01:04:08,561 --> 01:04:11,479
You look like
you have much on your mind.

996
01:04:11,562 --> 01:04:12,978
Not at all.

997
01:04:14,103 --> 01:04:15,729
Well, we're friends...

998
01:04:15,771 --> 01:04:19,188
