1100
01:10:43,429 --> 01:10:45,721
Hi there.
Here we go.

1101
01:10:45,762 --> 01:10:48,721
This is somebody that lives
in the same building. Thank you.

1102
01:10:48,762 --> 01:10:50,929
Are you Nancy Pong?

1103
01:10:52,305 --> 01:10:54,430
