1123
01:12:36,104 --> 01:12:38,520
No, no, no, you're wrong.

1124
01:12:44,772 --> 01:12:46,688
And another thing.

1125
01:12:49,313 --> 01:12:50,730
This Wendy...

1126
01:12:52,855 --> 01:12:56,065
she's nothing but a poor man's Mary.

1127
01:13:25,816 --> 01:13:27,233
