1128
01:13:32,858 --> 01:13:34,608
I'd better go.

1129
01:13:40,026 --> 01:13:41,984
I'll walk you to the door.

1130
01:13:42,026 --> 01:13:44,984
- That's all right. Stay there.
- No, it's okay.

1131
01:13:47,318 --> 01:13:49,734
- Wait.
- Take your time. You all right?

1132
01:13:56,235 --> 01:13:59,152
Thanks for tonight.
I know that I was a mess.

1133
01:13:59,235 --> 01:14:02,444
